"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/SLK-f3RAu-3a8vwQfzoAH.png?height=573&width=1198)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/ethersole/status/1463537481358491650](https://twitter.com/ethersole/status/1463537481358491650)\\n\\nDopex Buying & Staking 101 Chart with upwards trend\\n\\nThis thread will cover:\\n\\n* Buying $DPX\\n* Staking $DPX & $rDPX\\n* Compounding and Claiming those sweet rewards\\n\\n**\\\\*\\\\*This content may result in financial freedom and instant Chad syndrome so reader beware…**\\n\\nBest way to buy $DPX:\\n\\n* Get $ETH\\n* Bridge $ETH to Arbitrum via <https://bridge.arbitrum.io>\\n* Wait \\\\~10 mins for $ETH -> Arb network\\n* Head to <https://app.sushi.com/swap>\\n* Swap $ETH -> $DPX\\n* Sit back and realize you’re a chad now\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*This works for buying $rDPX as well\\n\\nHow to stake:\\n\\n* Head to the ‘Farms’ tab on the Dapp: <https://app.dopex.io/farms>\\n* Deposit into any of the 4 farms (pictured below)\\n* \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JiRp4q1ztPdaHDjqxkfRT.jfif?height=1668&width=3112)\\n\\nChoosing the best farm for you: \\n\\n\\\\- Single Side [$DPX](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24DPX&src=cashtag_click): Chad DPX bull \\n\\n\\\\- Single Side [$rDPX](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24rDPX&src=cashtag_click): Chad rDPX bull \\n\\n\\\\- DPX/ETH farm: Chad but still loves ETH \\n\\n\\\\- rDPX/ETH farm: Chad but still loves ETH \\n\\nIL isn’t a huge concern since these farms yield such juicy rewards.\\n\\nClaiming: On the same ‘Farms’ tab you will see a ‘Claim’ button show up after you stake your assets. In order to see accrued rewards you will click that ‘Claim’ button. How often you claim/compound rewards is up to you!! Always factor gas costs so they don’t eat into your ROI.\",\"timestamp\":1641680238,\"title\":\"项目：Dopex\"},\"digest\":\"BzitXWsxFel87ymVgybFPrM8aRpHDQ1mJjRS_-Xqn3g\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd8E93E06a84581c10DC1F9F60ec91f0F38994f1b\",\"